  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1867-04-09">April 9th '67</date>
      <name type="place">Jackson River Va</name>
     </dateline>
     <salute>Dr Sir</salute>
    </opener>

    <p>I wish you can do it that you would send me out a dozen or two hands. Or at least let it be
     known that I want hands. I want ten or a dozen for choppin whom I will pay $15 per and 8 or 10
     common hands whom I will pay 12 The chopper to go to Millboro &amp; the other hands here </p>
    <p> If you can do anything that way I will be obliged-- </p>
    <p> I send you with this the paper regardin Mr. Fulty </p>

    <closer>
     <salute>Truly Yours</salute>
     <signed>C.Clay</signed>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
 </text>
